{"title_page": "List of Good Morning Britain presenters", "text_new": "{{update|date=June 2017}}\nThis is a list of the on-air team members for the [[ITV Breakfast]] programme [[Good Morning Britain (2014 TV programme)|Good Morning Britain]] which began broadcasting in the United Kingdom on 28 April 2014.\n\nOn 3 March 2014 it was announced that Sean Fletcher, Charlotte Hawkins, Susanna Reid and Ben Shephard would become the presenters. Piers Morgan joined in 2015.\n\nFrom March 2020 (due to the COVID-19 pandemic) sister show [[Lorraine (TV programme)|Lorraine]] was cancelled so presenter [[Lorraine Kelly]] joined as the host of the new fourth hour of Good Morning Britain\n\n==Presenters==\n\n===Main Presenters/Newsreaders===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"margin:1em 1em 1em 0; background:#f9f9f9; border:1px #aaa solid; border-collapse:collapse; font-size:90%;\" border=\"2\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"4\" \n|- align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#ffe87c\"\n! <span style=\"color:black\">Tenure(s)</span> !! <span style=\"color:black\">Person</span> !! <span style=\"color:black\">Current Title</span> !! <span style=\"color:black\">Related notes</span>\n|-\n|2014\u2013 ||[[Susanna Reid]] || Monday\u2013Thursday Presenter || rowspan=\"2\" | \n|-\n|2015\u2013 ||[[Piers Morgan]] || Monday\u2013Wednesday Presenter\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\" |2014\u2013 ||[[Ben Shephard]] || Thursday\u2013Friday Presenter || Previously Monday/Tuesday & Thursday/Friday presenter (2014-2015)\n|-\n|[[Kate Garraway]] || Thursday Newsreader & Friday Presenter (Monday-Thursday Presenter During School Holidays) || Previously Thursday Presenter (2014) then Monday-Wednesday & Friday presenter (2015)\n|-\n|[[Charlotte Hawkins]] || Monday\u2013Wednesday, Friday Newsreader & Deputy Presenter. || Previously Friday presenter (2014)\n|-\n|[[Laura Tobin]] || Main Weather Presenter || \n|-\n|[[Alex Beresford]] || Deputy Weather Presenter || Also ITV Weather presenter\n|}\n\n=== Editors/Relief Presenters ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Tenure(s)\n!Person\n!Current Title\n!Related Notes\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" |2014-\n|[[Sean Fletcher]]\n|Relief Newsreader\n|Previously presenter & Sports Editor (2014)\n|-\n|[[Ranvir Singh]]\n|Political Editor & Wednesday Newsreader\n|Previously Friday Newsreader (2014-2016) & Thursday Newsreader (2015)\n|-\n|[[Richard Arnold (presenter)|Richard Arnold]]\n|Entertainment Editor\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |2018-\n|[[Richard Madeley]]\n|Main Relief Presenter<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hellomagazine.com/film/2017101843303/richard-madeley-confirms-gmb-role/|title=Richard Madeley confirms Good Morning Britain role|date=2017-10-18|website=HELLO!|language=en|access-date=2019-05-24}}</ref>\n|Monday-Wednesday Relief Presenter\n|-\n|[[Adil Ray]]\n|Deputy Relief Presenter<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ok.co.uk/tv/daytime/good-morning-britain-adil-ray-14321065|title=Adil Ray Good Morning Britain: Who is Adil Ray? Citizen Khan actor joins ITV show|last=Donaldson|first=Laura|date=2018-10-30|website=OK! Magazine|access-date=2019-05-24}}</ref>\n|Thursday-Friday Relief Presenter\n|}\n\n== 6AM Presenters ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Tenure(s)\n!Person\n!Days Presenting\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" |2020-\n|[[Charlotte Hawkins]]\n|Monday, Tuesday & Friday\n|-\n|[[Ranvir Singh]]\n|Wednesday\n|-\n|[[Kate Garraway]]\n|Thursday\n|}\n\n== Former Presenters/Editors ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+Former Presenters/Editors\n!Tenure\n!Person\n!Title\n|-\n|2014-2015\n|[[John Stapleton (English journalist)|John Stapleton]]\n|Former Wednesday Presenter (Became Wednesday Newsreader)\n|-\n|2014-2015\n|Sue Jameson \n|Former Political Editor\n|-\n|2016-2018\n|[[Jeremy Kyle]]\n|Former Main Relief Presenter \n|}\n\n==Guest presenters==\n<!-- DO NOT ADD John Stapleton or Kate Garraway to this list as he was a relief presenter not a guest presenter-->\n{{col-start}}\n{{col-3}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"margin:1em 1em 1em 0; background:#f9f9f9; border:1px #aaa solid; border-collapse:collapse; 